  "texts": [
    "Among the four datasets, FPB 2 and OTT-QA foot_1 lack a published test split.",
    "TAT-QA foot_2 has a test split without gold labels.",
    "WikiSQL foot_3 provides a public test set.",
    "We used the WikiSQL test split, and for the other 3 datasets generated random 80-10-10 splits (available here).",
    "Table 1 summarises the statistics of the datasets."
